OL,7,FA father who was almost killed by a
OL,8,Fspeeding car in is pleading for
OL,9,Fdrivers in the city to follow the
OL,10,Frules of the road before more lives
OL,11,Fare lost.
OL,13,FStephen Andoh was inches away from
OL,14,Fdeath after he was hit by an out-of-
OL,15,Fcontrol car last May.
OL,17,FHe was working a regular night shift
OL,18,Fas a security guard, when a speeding
OL,19,Fcar, driving in a 30mph zone, smashed
OL,20,Finto the building where he was stood
OL,21,Fin Witton.
