OL,7,FMr Andoh miraculously escaped with his
OL,8,Flife, but not without injury.
OL,10,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV News
OL,11,FCentral, Mr Andoh said: "I never saw
OL,12,Fthe car coming, I didn't see the car
OL,13,Fcoming at all...walking back to the
OL,14,Foffice, before I realised I was in
OL,15,Fsharp pain, really sharp pain, and I
OL,16,Fwas bleeding from my nose and my leg."
