OL,7,FMr Andoh was hospitalised for nine
OL,8,Fdays, suffering leg injuries which
OL,9,Fstopped him from working for eight
OL,10,Fmonths. He still has to take four
OL,11,Ftablets a day for his recovery.
OL,13,FHe added: "I'm not as I was before. My
OL,14,Fmobility, it has affected my mobility.
OL,15,FI still got blood clots in my lungs
OL,16,Fand my legs, so it's a struggle. I
OL,17,Fcan't do things that I used to do
OL,18,Fbefore".
OL,20,FMr Andoh said he struggles to do the
OL,21,Fthings he used to
