OL,7,FMr Andoh's daughter, Levlyn, says the
OL,8,Fmental scars of nearly losing her
OL,9,Ffather have only just started to sink
OL,10,Fin.
OL,12,FShe said: "A couple of months after
OL,13,Fthe accident, it really got to me, I
OL,14,Fkind of isolated myself - would only
OL,15,Fgo see my dad. There was more of a
OL,16,Ffear that I almost lost him, I was
OL,17,Fthis close to losing my dad, it kind
OL,18,Fof rocks your world, it's something
OL,19,Fyou can't comprehend on a daily basis."
