OL,7,FShe added: "I also get nervous being
OL,8,Fon the road myself, walking around,
OL,9,Ftaking the bus, like, is someone going
OL,10,Fto come off the road and hit me?"
OL,12,FLevlyn said nearly losing her dad
OL,13,F'rocked her world'
OL,15,FMr Andoh's case of a dangerous
OL,16,Fspeeding driver echoes recent scenes
OL,17,Fwitnessed on Queslett Road in
OL,18,FBirmingham, as well as a crash on Soho
OL,19,FRoad in which an alleged speeding
OL,20,Fdriver hit a series of cars.
