OL,7,FMr Andoh said: "It brought back my
OL,8,Fmemory, I really felt for the guy that
OL,9,Flost his life. I feel sorry for the
OL,10,Ffamily. I know what they are going
OL,11,Fthrough now, and I'm really sorry for
OL,12,Fthe family - it brought back memories,
OL,13,Fand every day it brings memories, it
OL,14,Freally really does."
OL,16,FWest Midlands Police confirmed that no
OL,17,Farrests have been made in Mr Andoh's
OL,18,Fcase - though he and his daughter are
OL,19,Fnow urging drivers to stick to speed
OL,20,Flimits.
