OL,7,FThey said: "Drivers should take
OL,8,Fresponsibility, they should be aware
OL,9,Fthere are lives on the street. People
OL,10,Fhave got children that are looking up
OL,11,Fto their father, and when they go to
OL,12,Fwork and can't come back home - it's
OL,13,Fsad. Drivers need to take
OL,14,Fresponsibility... I just feel like it
OL,15,Fneeds to stop, this careless driving."
OL,17,FThe par hope that drivers heed their
OL,18,Fwarning - slow down before you take
OL,19,Fsomeone's life.
