OL,7,FA spokesperson for West Midlands
OL,8,FPolice said: "We were called to a
OL,9,Fcollision at the junction of Birch
OL,10,FRoad and Cheshire Road just before
OL,11,F11.45pm on 17 May last year".
OL,13,F"One man has attended a voluntary
OL,14,Finterview where he was questioned
OL,15,Funder caution on suspicion of causing
OL,16,Fserious injury by careless driving. We
OL,17,Fare in the process of gathering
OL,18,Fevidence, including medical reports,
OL,19,Fand our investigation continues".
